data.description: Location! Location! Location! This 3-bedrooms, 2 bathrooms in Algiers is the great place to call your own. The house boasts a large backyard with a shed for outdoor entertaining or just relaxing. Newer roof,  NO CARPET, granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances.  The home is centrally located in Algiers easy access to the Downtown and West Bankexpressway.   The New Orleans City Soft Second Program grant can be used on this home. Seller is willing to offer $5000.00 towards closing cost and prepaid with a reasonable offer for buyer.
